    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Large circular boards, usually of cork and having numbered compartments, used as targets during the game of darts.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
